The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person who growsiris is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | time-travel |
| Nationality   | mexican    | pakistani   |
| Sport         | volleyball | sailing     |
| Flower     | zinnia | iris  |

